<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 90. Median lobe of male genitalia, right-lateral, ventral, left-lateral, dorsal views of Dasiosoma quadraticolle sp. n., holotype." , "Figures 55 - 60. Type materials, scale bars = 2.0 mm: 55 Holotype of Dasiosoma sudanicum Basilewsky 56 Holotype of Dasiosoma ivorense Basilewsky 57 Holotype of Diamella indica Kirschenhofer [= Dasiosoma indicum (Kirschenhofer)] 58 Paratype of Lachnoderma maindroni Tian & Deuve [= Dasiosoma maindroni (Tian & Deuve)] 59 Lectotype of Singlis hirsutus Bates [= Dasiosoma hirsutum (Bates)] 60 The \" lectotype \" designated by Tian & Deuve, 2001 for Singlis hirsutus Bates." , "Figure 87. Median lobe of male genitalia, right-lateral, ventral, left-lateral, dorsal views of Dasiosoma bellum (Habu), a specimen from Vietnam." , "Figure 86. Median lobe of male genitalia, right-lateral, ventral, left-lateral, dorsal views of Dasiosoma ivorense Basilewsky, a paratype from Cote d'Ivoire." , "Figures 61 - 66. Type materials, scale bars = 2.0 mm: 61 Holotype of Dasiosoma quadraticolle sp. n. 62 Lectotype of Endynomena lewisii Bates [= Orionella lewisii (Bates)] 63 Holotype of Orionella obenbergi Jedlicka [= Orionella lewisii (Bates)] 64 Holotype of Endynomena discoidalis Bates [= Orionella discoidalis (Bates)] 65 Lectotype of Plochionus pradieri Fairmaire [= Endynomena pradieri (Fairmaire)] 66 Lectotype of Saronychium inconspicuum Blackburn [= Endynomena pradieri (Fairmaire)]." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/29683" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/29704" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/29684" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/29708" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/29705" .

